data.description: Amazing opportunity to own in Nawney Creek North in Pungo on 3 acres; horses, chickens & goats allowed. Country living with modern amenities! No flood insurance required.  Home features a quiet cul-de-sac lot located next to a wooded lot designated as a park.  Large wrapped front porch, screened in porch, LG deck, exterior shed, firepit and swing.  Eat-in kitchen w/ ceramic floors, wood cabinets, SS appliances and pantry.  Fam RM w/ wood burning FP, large LIV RM & DR.  Mud RM w/ utility closet & 1/2 Bath.  4 BRMS & 2 full baths upstairs. Primary BDRM has walk-in closet with an ensuite bathroom which includes jacuzzi tub, walk-in shower, ceramic tile & double sinks. Attached 2 car GAR includes 220V & Generator Hookup. Well pump & pressure tank replaced 2021.  Pool liner & pump to be replaced prior to closing.  Beaches, boat ramps, Red Mill Commons Shopping Mall & fresh produce markets are nearby. Kellam HS & PA Middle schools.
